---
const DOWNLOAD_URL = 'https://github.com/ArekkMirmun/GeneradorExamenesEvau/releases/latest';
---

<section id="descarga" class="py-24 sm:py-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-50/60 to-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Preparado para practicar</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
      Descarga la herramienta y empieza a generar exámenes de práctica con ejercicios reales de Selectividad.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <a
        href={DOWNLOAD_URL}
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-5 rounded-xl transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal-600/25 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        <span>⬇</span> Descargar GeneradorExamenes.zip
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust data -->
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
      <span>📚 1586 ejercicios</span>
      <span>📅 Convocatorias 2018–2025</span>
      <span>📄 Formato oficial EvAU</span>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-amber-700 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
      <span>⚠️</span> Requiere Windows — no compatible con Mac ni Linux
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
